        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🟩 Green-Screen Compositor\n\nKey out a green background and composite your subject over any clip — deterministic chroma key, no AI.\n\n**Pipeline:** Subject (on green) → chroma key → overlay onto background → output.\n\n**Try this:** set `key_color` to your screen color, raise `similarity` if green fringes remain, and use `x`/`y`/`scale` on Overlay to place the subject."
